Rating: 3
This is an excellent, very tasty recipe and extremely easy to make. I added 1 tsp of chaat masala seasoning to give it a bit of an Indian flavour. Hazelnut oil and walnut oil are easily damaged/oxidized by heat and are therefore suitable for cold use only, not for cooking. I would use either butter or extra virgin olive oil.

